Package: taifacare
Type: Package
Title: Universal Health Coverage Data Transformation and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Maangi", email = "daniel.maangi@apeiro.digital.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for fetching, transforming, and analysing
    universal health coverage (UHC) data from UHC Data Lake Gold Layer
    in ClickHouse. Covers ERP payment claims (old and new) and provider
    registries, with parameterised query functions and tidy summarisation 
    helpers.
